{
  "2145880": {
    "name": "Horde",
    "steam_appid": 2145880,
    "required_age": "18",
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145880/extras/c0c6c1bf0bd9c3a3e3ea140f8de10a06.avif?t=1768678468\" width=800 height=258 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Civilization has fallen.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join the Horde, launch yourself to the Zone and die purging the Hellspawn invasion in the humanity's last stand while competing for the highest scored <strong>Hellruns</strong> on the official leaderboards with other players!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145880/extras/be334a415d396a8657eb290eea3705f0.avif?t=1768678468\" width=800 height=100 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hordes signature <i>Ultraviolent gameplay</i> combined with 2.5D physics will put a smile even on the most conservative face. Shoot, slice, burn, electrocute, blow-up and pulverize hundreds of enemies at the same time. Combining kills also adds score multiplier (and makes you look like a pro). </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145880/extras/bf6f2db9da6a050612d5e7251ca03917.avif?t=1768678468\" width=800 height=100 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each <i>Hellrun</i> is divided to different Zones, that need to be purged from the Hellspawn to advance into the next one. Typical <i>Hellrun</i> only takes a few minutes. Perfect time killer for a coffee break or when <u>skipping work</u>!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145880/extras/a8c29fd26d014d5912d01fb87c262d5a.avif?t=1768678468\" width=800 height=100 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Anti-social, single played multiplayer experience! Challenge other players directly in <strong><i>THE RETRIBUTION</i></strong> mode and beat their <i>Hellrun </i>scores asynchronously. Online leaderboards and punishing daily challenges included as well!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145880/extras/a1a3283bd7e85f4134b677231b7d495d.avif?t=1768678468\" width=800 height=100 /></span> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Permadeath, seed based procedurally generated gameplay, dynamic weather, incredible realistic violence modeling and 2.5D physics combined with huge variety of weapons, enemies, power-ups, maps, secrets and bosses will give bang for your buck while keeping you busy! </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145880/extras/30a361555ebe2c9df7a37fdccc6b4499.avif?t=1768678468\" width=800 height=100 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Just like in the good ol' days! Think Doom, Alien Breed, Hotline Miami and Tetris had a baby on steroids. </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145880/extras/cb1a808337704b37687a54135679412e.avif?t=1768678468\" width=800 height=100 /></span></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" > </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We guarantee: The combination of acid house, techno and game tunes from the 80's and the 90's will make the killing as easy as breathing.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145880/extras/d6908a0fe1097f7a2b7dec4e034d165d.avif?t=1768678468\" width=800 height=100 /></span> </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Remember the times when video games whooped everyone's asses? Those days are back: Stand your ground and fight! </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2145880/extras/84f16eeab602cf7eca6c4cb96ec2ea16.avif?t=1768678468\" width=800 height=100 /></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buy the ticket, take the ride. Horde will be fully released in 2026.</p></li></ul>",
